Modupe Adeyeye listen (amụrụ na 29 Julaị 1992) bụ onye England na-eme ihe nkiri na ihe nlerẹanya, nke a maara maka ọrụ ya dị ka Faith Olubunmi na EastEnders na EastEndors: E20 na Blessing Chambers na Hollyoakslisten (help·info)

A mụrụ ya ma zụlite ya na London, aha ya "Modupe" pụtara "M na-eto ma ọ bụ na-ekele Chineke" na Yoruba. Ọ pụtara na usoro ihe nkiri Our Girl and My Murder, yaṅa ndị dọkịta. O mechara pụta na ihe nkiri 2014 Honeytrap, n'akụkụ onye bụbu onye E20 Tosin Cole.

Na 21 Febụwarị 2014, Adeyeye sonyeere ndị na-eme ihe nkiri Hollyoaks dị ka Blessing Chambers, e mechara kpughee na àgwà ya bụ transgender. Blessing malitere mmekọrịta ya na Dennis Savage (Joe Tracini), ma mesịa chọta onwe ya na nwunye Dennis nwụrụ aṅwụ Leanne Holiday (Jessica Forrest) na-asọ mpi, onye ajọ onye na-edina mmadụ n'ike bụ Finn O'Connor (Keith Rice) wakporo ya n'ụzọ obi ọjọọ wee malite imerụ onwe ya ahụ mgbe ezinụlọ ya gọnahụrụ ya maka ịbụ transgender. Ọ pụtara n'oge ikpeazụ ya na 21 Nọvemba 2014. N'afọ 2020, Adeyeye ga-apụta na ihe nkiri telivishọn BBC Surge as Mischa
